{"tid":448460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共持續打壓　香港護照排名繼續不敵星日韓","createTime":"2017-10-26T08:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T09:59:16.000Z","uid":82640,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"74bcbb1e80ae8896660a8304aa5038be0c946990","tid":448460,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"金融顧問公司Arton Capital周三（25日）公布「全球護照排名」，<span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡以總分159分成為「最強」護照</span>，是首次有亞洲國家獨佔鰲頭。Arton Capital今年較早前曾評定新加坡和德國的護照平分秋色，惟德國今次以一分之差屈居第二；<span style=\"color: red;\">香港特區護照就以142分排行16</span>。<br />\n<br />\n「最強」護照：新加坡<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171025/photo/bkn-20171025173646755-1025_00822_001_02b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171025%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171025173646755-1025_00822_001_02b.jpg&h=9b244257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與新加坡護照相比，香港特區護照連中國也不可進入<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/164049_c0b207f9632b9100bb535b1a788c21cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F164049_c0b207f9632b9100bb535b1a788c21cc.jpg&h=98084634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港於今次排名中是以香港特區護照作比較，並非部分港人持有的BNO護照。<br />\n<br />\n該排行榜是按照各國護照的免簽證積分排列，積分愈高代表護照持有者可在更多國家享有入境免簽待遇，或可辦理落地簽證，過去多年，榜首位置多由歐洲國家奪得。"},{"pid":"37753e652ff52c593326a9c6a6c428c60169f3ed","tid":448460,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"台灣呢"},{"pid":"819b65b3d2bedc9785cc37e491606106b1790181","tid":448460,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣呢</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.passportindex.org/byRank.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passportindex.org%2FbyRank.php&d=j8M6UL9r%2BYhbQd%2FflA0DHr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=94cca88f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.passportindex.o