"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881b42ed0af0a9287fff0679b1700093fb151c9b","tid":448460,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"香港護照冇美國免簽注定低十幾格<br />\n<br />\n仲有揸香港護照旅行出事就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d2a2b9817bd284d6532e282d23b37732352141","tid":448460,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似無計BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBNO高少少<br />\n有好多HKSAR免但BNO冇 例 : 俄佬</blockquote><br />\n揸晒兩本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記著<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣唔受雙重國藉</span>, 用開一本就要用死一本入台。</blockquote><br />\n5年前用CNO入<br />\n今年用BNO入<br />\n彈出彈入都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講用死一本嗰啲<br />\n我懷疑連過關都唔撚識過<br />\n<br />\n紅字直情係笑話<br />\n台灣先周街派護照俾華人血統球員、科學家<br />\n全部都係雙重國藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d96e6d7d9b569ee264958e7a6bd2c82123b074","tid":448460,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似無計BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBNO高少少<br />\n有好多HKSAR免但BNO冇 例 : 俄佬</blockquote><br />\n揸晒兩本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記著<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣唔受雙重國藉</span>, 用開一本就要用死一本入台。</blockquote><br />\n5年前用CNO入<br />\n今年用BNO入<br />\n彈出彈入都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講用死一本嗰啲<br />\n我懷疑連過關都唔撚識過<br />\n<br />\n紅字直情係笑話<br />\n台灣先周街派護照俾華人血統球員、科學家<br />\n全部都係雙重國藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你無台灣國藉邊個得閒理你拎幾多本護照"},{"pid":"a6754dcb37b70f422caa63508b98edb70ffa76ef","tid":448460,"uid":61728,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:48:22.000Z","msg":"一直都話香港真係好慘<br />\n<br />\n香港治安好<br />\n人口少<br />\n夠西化+識下D英文<br />\n國際金融中心<br />\n宗教自由+冇同任何地區有歷史問題(除左中國)<br />\n<br />\n如果香港係一個國家，護照好用程度排第一都完全唔覺得怪<br />\n新加坡性質同香港差不多，已經係全球第一好用<br />\n就算係韓國之流既國家，本野都已經超越日本<br />\n<br />\n香港作為一個高度發展地區<br />\n係唯一一個冇得美國簽證既地方<br />\n護照好用程度連東歐落後國家都不如"},{"pid":"841a8e839e5ad9f04f2b3d78caff06a9ee1820b6","tid":448460,"uid":61728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實用簡單多數係好唔Make Sense, 唔好話美國, 單係加澳免簽, 價值就足以大過全非洲免簽</blockquote><br />\n非洲免簽勁好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地要簽證好多時係因為想要你筆申請費<br />\n如果你個國家帶比佢既利益遠高於筆錢仲要關係好好先可以免簽(好似係)<br />\n<br />\nbtw俄羅斯都係數一數二好少比人免簽既國家<br />\n而冇記錯韓國係唯一(定係極少數)可以同時免簽美國同俄國既地方"},{"pid":"298a02eef89c1048fb66c63bc9930147ad8887b9","tid":448460,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"長氣d講埋<br />\n<br />\n其實我地係唔係應該叫英國盡返責任，主動幫BNO搞免簽?<br />\n英國係幾年前宣佈唔會再主動為BNO爭取免簽<br />\n但我認為依個係英國既責任<br />\n如果連依少少野都做唔到/香港人連少少都唔叫英國盡責<br />\n咁本BNO就真係完全冇咩用"},{"pid":"764719308811a281469bbbc98fd6367cb9a3a611","tid":448460,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T18:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/180237_e49feac9b5b904ee7dcf130ae4271aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F180237_e49feac9b5b904ee7dcf130ae4271aa5.jpg&h=4339cae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img